A small architect architectural firm wants a compact printer with built in Wi-Fi and ePrinting
capabilities to print from anywhere. Which printer should you recommend?
A. T120 ePrinter
B. T790ps ePrinter
C. T1300ps ePrinter
D. Z2100 Printer
Answer: A
Which printers have an automatic firmware update feature that helps the customer future
proof their printer and take advantage of updates from HP?
A. all HP Designjet printers
B. all PostScript printers
C. all Z series printers
D. All ePrinters
Answer: C
Reference:http://www.hp.com/hpinfo/newsroom/press_kits/2013/HPatPRINT13/Z5400_Ne
wsAdvisory_FINAL.pdf(page 2, first para)

A. printing from front USB slot
B. wireless networking
C. self-help animations
D. HP Designjet ePrint & Share
Answer: D

In addition to two online rolls with smart switching and roll protection, which other feature
does the HP Designjet T1300ps offer?
A. printing on two rolls at the same time
B. media length tracking
C. roll usage reports
D. dual roll printing
Answer: B,C

(Select two.)
A. two online rolls
B. LED printer speed
C. large 300cc Matte Black cartridge
D. affordable personal printer
E. double swath technology
Answer: A,B
